headline: Ametek: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The average estimate of eight analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for earnings of $1.76 per share. The maker of electronic instruments and electromechanical devices posted revenue of $1.89 billion in the period, also beating Street forecasts. Five analysts surveyed by Zacks expected $1.82 billion.
